d and edited by the late John O Crown and Joseph W Crown for more than 33 years Entered at the Post office at Berry tllle Va as secondclass mail mat ter 8150 Per If car In Advance MILITARY PAGEANT IN NATIONS CAPITAL SOON Visitors to the Nations capital during the fourth week of Septem ber will have an opportunity to wit ness one of the most stirring Military Pageants that takes place in this or any other country according to Col Leon B Komer of the Army War College there The spacious grounds of the Army War College at historical Washing ton Barracks is a most fitting setting for the Annual Military Exposition and Carnival which will be hV September 25 26 and 27 At season of the year Washington is most beautiful the weather clear bracing and mellow with the rich ness of autumn Washington Bar racks borders on and is almost sur rounedd by the the beautl ful Potomac Inauguated three years ago the gerat Army show has become an an nual event that draws thousands of visitors to Washington It is"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-09-28T23:53:50.775Z", "group": ["ndnp/vi", "library-of-virginia-richmond-va-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn85025371/1930-09-18/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:vi:batch_vi_moser_ver01:data:sn85025371:00542867322:1930091801:0724/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=465&w=323", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:vi:batch_vi_moser_ver01:data:sn85025371:00542867322:1930091801:0724/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=931&w=647", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/vi/batch_vi_moser_ver01/data/sn85025371/00542867322/1930091801/0724.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["clarke county", "clarke", "berryville", "virginia", "united states"], "location_city": ["berryville"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["clarke"], "location_state": ["virgini